# Linear Integration Rules

When creating Linear issues:
- **Always use project**: "Mockifyer" (or "mockifyer" if case-sensitive)
- **Default labels**: "feature" and "backlog" should be applied by default
- When creating issues via Linear MCP tools, always include:
  - `project: "Mockifyer"` (or the exact project name/ID)
  - `labels: ["feature", "backlog"]` unless explicitly overridden by the user
- If the user specifies different labels or project, use their preferences instead
- When searching for projects, prioritize finding "Mockifyer" project
